The paper deals with matchings and graphs, which are topics in discrete mathematics (cs.DM) and graph theory (cs.GT). The main focus of the paper is on trees (cs.DS), and the paper presents a new decomposition algorithm for trees (cs.CG). The paper also discusses a parameter related to matchings, which could be considered a combinatorial optimization problem (cs.DC).
